Babcock up on bullish weekend press report . Shares in Babcock International , in a downward spiral for more than a year , climbed 8 - 1 / 2p to 63p by 0911 GMT on Monday following weekend press reports quoting a bullish Merrill Lynch analyst , dealers said . The Sunday Times quoted Merrill Lynch ' s engineering analyst Paul Compton as saying Babcock ' s acquisition of Rosyth naval dockyard from the government should be a big boost for Babcock . Additionally , he forecast stronger half year profits from Babcock , due to release its results later this month . - - Debra Sherman , London newsroom + 44 171 542 4026 
